  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/createml\/mlrandomforestclassifier\/modelparameters-swift.struct\ncrawled: 2025-12-14T13:53:50Z\n---\n\n# MLRandomForestClassifier.ModelParameters\n\n**Structure**\n\nParameters that affect the process of training a model.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstruct ModelParameters\n```\n\n## Creating parameters\n\n- **init(validation:maxDepth:maxIterations:minLossReduction:minChildWeight:randomSeed:rowSubsample:columnSubsample:)**\n- **init(validationData:maxDepth:maxIterations:minLossReduction:minChildWeight:randomSeed:rowSubsample:columnSubsample:)**: Creates a new set of parameters.\n- **MLRandomForestClassifier.ModelParameters.ValidationData**: Values for specifying validation data.\n\n## Accessing parameters\n\n- **columnSubsample**: Must be in the range (0, 1).\n- **maxDepth**\n- **maxIterations**\n- **minChildWeight**\n- **minLossReduction**\n- **randomSeed**\n- **rowSubsample**: Must be in the range (0, 1).\n- **validationData**: Validation data represented as a `MLDataTable`.\n- **validation**: Validation data.\n\n## Describing parameters\n\n- **description**: A text representation of the model parameters for a random forest classifier.\n- **debugDescription**: A text representation of the model parameters for a random forest classifier that’s suitable for output during debugging.\n- **playgroundDescription**: A description of the model parameters for a random forest classifier shown in a playground.\n\n## Default Implementations\n\n- **CustomDebugStringConvertible Implementations**\n- **CustomPlaygroundDisplayConvertible Implementations**\n- **CustomStringConvertible Implementations**\n\n## Inspecting a random forest classifier\n\n- **model**: The Core ML model.\n- **modelParameters**: The underlying parameters used when training the model.\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- Copyable\n- CustomDebugStringConvertible\n- CustomPlaygroundDisplayConvertible\n- CustomStringConvertible\n\n",
